| Time | Activity |
|------|----------|
| T0 | Multiple failed login attempts generated |
| T1 | Event ID 4625 collected by Azure Monitor Agent |
| T2 | Events forwarded to Log Analytics Workspace |
| T3 | Microsoft Sentinel Analytics Rule executed |
| T4 | Alert generated for investigation |

